  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/b42bde5a3ba17d44b63dfe8a810196bc.poster.avif?t=1764828084\" width=614 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/b42bde5a3ba17d44b63dfe8a810196bc.webm?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/b42bde5a3ba17d44b63dfe8a810196bc.mp4?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eldritch Exterminators</strong> is a bullet heaven rogue-lite where heroes don’t exist—just guns. Wield a possessed infernal weapon and unleash chaos on endless hordes of Elder God minions. Master a deep upgrade system, forging devastating builds with soul-shredding firepower. Your mission? Slay an Eldritch God and break free from its cursed grip. Do you have the grit to break free?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/033ba6fb6cc44c63bdffab45d2f05f75.poster.avif?t=1764828084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/033ba6fb6cc44c63bdffab45d2f05f75.webm?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/033ba6fb6cc44c63bdffab45d2f05f75.mp4?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/2cbe829efd9e5f30af70865637c57a74.poster.avif?t=1764828084\" width=614 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/2cbe829efd9e5f30af70865637c57a74.webm?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/2cbe829efd9e5f30af70865637c57a74.mp4?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INFERNAL ARMAMENTS</strong> | Unleash chaos as the embodiment of a Gun, laying waste to hordes with a hail of bullets! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SOULS </strong>| Embody the tormented souls consumed by the Eldritch Gods. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RUNES </strong>| Experiment with ancient runes and strategically customize your playstyle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REVELATIONS </strong>| Unveil an extensive array of Guns, Souls, Abilities, and Runes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRIBULATIONS </strong>| Confront harrowing challenges and test your mettle against the true might of the Eldritch Gods! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARTIFACTS </strong>| Discover a variety of artifacts that offer unique properties, not just stats. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/ff608fc1c9da2b5964bf3fa47ac2facd.poster.avif?t=1764828084\" width=614 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493910/extras/ff608fc1c9da2b5964bf3fa47ac2facd.webm?t=1764828084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
